    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Roadhog holds an angle and lands Chain Hook on an isolated target, following up with a point-blank Scrap Gun blast before retreating to heal off the trade with Take a Breather.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>He has no barrier and limited team utility beyond the hook pick, so if the hook whiffs he's committed his cooldown and is exposed as one of the squishier tanks in a straight fight.</p>"
